        principle: "Yeh ek industrial-grade dishwasher ki tarah kaam karta hai. Glassware ko special racks aur injectors par load kiya jaata hai taaki paani har kone tak pahunch sake. Machine ek programmable cycle se guzarti hai: \n1.  **Pre-wash:** Thande paani se dhona.\n2.  **Wash:** Garam paani (60-85°C) aur **special lab-grade, low-foaming detergents** (jo alkaline ya acidic ho sakte hain) ko high-pressure jets se spray karke glassware ko saaf karna.\n3.  **Rinses:** Kai baar tap water se rinse karna.\n4.  **Final Rinse:** Ant mein, **purified water (Distilled ya Deionized - DI water)** se rinse karna. Yeh sabse mahatvapurna step hai, kyunki yeh sunishchit karta hai ki tap water ke minerals (salts) ka koi bhi residue glassware par na sookhe.\n5.  **Drying (Optional):** Kuch models garam hawa (70-110°C) se glassware ko sukha bhi dete hain.",
