            description: '**Types:**\n- Standard glass (13×100 mm, 16×150 mm)\n- Screw-cap (for liquid cultures)\n- Durham tubes (for gas detection)\n- Centrifuge tubes (conical/round bottom)\n**Use:** Conducting small-scale chemical reactions, heating samples, or growing bacterial cultures.'
